name: Conjunction - Alienflesh Landscape VI
description: Alienflesh Landscape x Quantum Planet collaboration with maxladabaumart (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1Xf8tih62ijfx4ATGyHgvEf8ULovQ6ikjV). Foreground landscape mutated from a crop of human flesh with multiple generations of AI DeepStyle style transfer. Planets created by maxladabaumart - Random quantum bits generated by energy level jumps in an atom are used to generate a random color grid. The random color grid is plugged into a homemade GAN trained on hundreds of pictures of planets
